Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正文
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.80,0:00:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惑星歼灭用武器?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.38,0:00:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N根据与Meister奈绪·张的高物质化请求一起送信而来的资料
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.10,0:00:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,判明那个是被叫做尤娜的旧时代的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.91,0:00:30.83,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,440)}看来是设计成Use被Call作Child的Subunit Monster来Get Astron的Power的Program
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.91,0:00:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是设计成使用被称作Child的子兽来获取星球的力量的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.91,0:00:30.83,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Astron：希腊语，源于占星术，可以理解为星星）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.53,0:00:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从而进化成这个星球最终极的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.88,0:00:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将一切都破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.44,0:01:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会造成这种情况?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.69,0:01:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只是推测
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.82,0:01:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于过于强大
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.25,0:01:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制作和控制都很困难
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.64,0:01:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能因此而被抛弃到宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.46,0:01:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话世界就…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.35,0:01:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,THE END啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.50,0:02:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么　会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.66,0:02:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了父亲大人以外
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.43,0:02:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我谁都不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.11,0:02:43.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}第四幕　连接着的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.38,0:02:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫米饭也很好吃哦　哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.31,0:03:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之　这是我试着用海里的素材制作出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.90,0:03:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能尝一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.30,0:03:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都这时候了你还真有创造性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.02,0:03:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是猫神拉面的新菜单呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.20,0:03:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦　尼娜　你醒过来啦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.59,0:03:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白陛下?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.41,0:03:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是空军武装基地　发射准备
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.25,0:03:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下等下　小女孩不要太自大啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.55,0:03:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下　出航要按顺序来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.95,0:03:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会等得下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.10,0:03:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.17,0:03:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要回到风花市去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.94,0:03:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱莉卡　你准备怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.03,0:04:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是要尽最大可能去寻找真白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照现在这样的情况　我也不能使用乙HiME的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.49,0:04:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.87,0:04:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市内我们加尔德罗贝会进行应对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.12,0:04:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.01,0:04:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.79,0:04:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey 爱莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.47,0:04:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加尔教授
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:15.37,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,440)}从Leader那来了Good News
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从头儿那来了好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.75,0:04:16.34,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,440)}Light
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.75,0:04:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.54,0:04:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂　来一下　我想和加尔德罗贝学院长取得联系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.53,0:04:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵循古老的传承　到达了这片土地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.43,0:04:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑之谷是连愕天王也无法跨越的暴风雨之彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还只是个无法看清的梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首领
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.91,0:04:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首领　是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.28,0:04:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有从真白那里来的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.25,0:04:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩　是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.31,0:04:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受困于被暴风雨封锁的岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.98,0:04:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点前来迎接
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.30,0:04:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.90,0:05:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶　还发生了这样的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.50,0:05:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩　那个　不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.18,0:05:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人全部都吃完了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.02,0:05:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你非常的饿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.56,0:05:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来　尼娜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.95,0:05:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱莉卡那家伙　有没有说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.56,0:05:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起　我并没有遇到爱莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.75,0:05:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱莉卡那家伙　究竟在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.48,0:05:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不知道我有多辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.49,0:05:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最可恨的是只有她的胸部在发育
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.20,0:05:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱莉卡不在　真白很寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.66,0:05:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.47,0:05:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.13,0:05:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了　不如尼娜你来成为我的乙HiME吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不　那个的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.13,0:05:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去散下步
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.17,0:05:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱莉卡　我们必须回去保护村子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.75,0:05:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一个人能行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.24,0:06:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的　谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.33,0:06:06.38,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,440)}爱莉卡　You已经成为了一个Good Brave了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.33,0:06:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱莉卡　你已经成为了一个优秀的勇者了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.70,0:06:07.33,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,440)}Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.70,0:06:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.56,0:06:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的　加尔教授
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.88,0:06:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就来啦　真白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.63,0:06:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是怎么办呢　我又游不远
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.89,0:06:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请给我苹果吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.64,0:06:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个不可思议的地方呢　黑之谷这地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.46,0:06:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是猫神大人教会我的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白陛下是不是讨厌爱莉卡了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.05,0:07:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶　没那回事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.42,0:07:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两人实际上关系可是非常好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.47,0:07:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯　所以才会吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.56,0:07:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们不仅是国王陛下和乙HiME　更是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.54,0:07:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真好啊　乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.52,0:07:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美丽　成熟　坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.60,0:07:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.56,0:07:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,获得力量是件非常可怕的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果走错一步的话　就会犯下无法挽回的过错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.33,0:07:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　那么是和这个一样的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.78,0:07:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.12,0:07:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.95,0:07:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山它…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.48,0:07:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山在鸣叫?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.37,0:07:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.38,0:08:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.41,0:08:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打破了结界的龙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.63,0:08:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白和尼娜她们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.21,0:08:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各国的情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.86,0:08:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾亚利兹　三角洲乙HiME部队　准备完成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.73,0:08:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路提希亚　罗姆尔斯及雷姆斯国境
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.48,0:08:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meister劳拉　Meister卡拉　准备完成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.65,0:08:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安南　Meister艾茵　准备完成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.62,0:08:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗洛林斯和卡尔迪亚也做好了攻击准备
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.67,0:08:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meister不在的国家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.53,0:08:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风花由Meister萨拉　阿尔泰由Meister玛雅负责
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.03,0:08:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人都到达预定位置
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.31,0:08:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Surrogate系统也准备就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.33,0:08:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随时都可以开始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.56,0:08:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯　如果攻击的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.50,0:09:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Child复活的可能性非常高
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.75,0:09:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果就这么等下去的话　总有一天也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就不如先下手为强
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.79,0:09:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是各国首脑的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.88,0:09:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿吾等得到真祖大人的加护...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.30,0:09:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.68,0:09:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对萨拉和玛雅进行认证送信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.80,0:09:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Surrogate系统启动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.03,0:09:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行认证吧　命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.89,0:09:26.89,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\4c&H272FFE&}{\3c&H1A72DE&}Materialise!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.02,0:09:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到后山避难去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.53,0:09:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真白陛下她…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然好像无法给予它致命的伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.30,0:10:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在复活之前能完全打倒它就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是让人不爽的花蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来晚了　Sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.40,0:10:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…
